==English==

===Etymology===
From {{etyl|grc}} {{term|sc=polytonic|σύμπτωμα|tr=sumptōma||a happening, accident, symptom of disease}} < stem of {{term|sc=polytonic|συμπίπτω|tr=sumpiptō||Ι befall}} < {{term|sc=polytonic|συν-|tr=sun-||together}} + {{term|sc=polytonic|πίπτω|tr=piptō||I fall}}.

===Noun===
{{en-noun}}

# {{medicine}} A [[perceived]] [[change]] in some [[function]], [[sensation]] or [[appearance]] of a [[person]] that [[indicates]] a [[disease]] or [[disorder]], such as [[fever]], [[headache]] or [[rash]].
# Anything that [[indicate]]s, or is [[characteristic]] of,  the [[presence]] of something else, especially of something undesirable.

